Package: QDRS
Type: Package
Title: Quantitative Disease Risk Score
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Danqing Xu
Maintainer: Danqing Xu <xud@pstat.ucsb.edu>
Description: Functions for calculating quantitative disease risk scores: 
    (1) Phenotype Risk Score (PheRS), (2) a spectral approach (Eigen), (3) principal component approaches (PCA) that include individual PCs and a linear combination of multiple PCs (LPC), (4), Non-negative Matrix Factorization with Rank 1 (NMF1), and (5) Latent Variable Score based on an unsupervised multivariate mixed model framework (LVS).
License: GPL-3
